<para style="p">A psalm of David, when he was in the wilderness of Judah.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />God, you are my God! I earnestly search for you,</para>

<para style="q1">my soul thirsts for you, and my flesh longs for you,</para>

<para style="q1">in a dry and weary land where there is no water.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />So I have looked on you in the holy people</para>

<para style="q1">to see your power and your glory.</para>
